\begin_layout Subsection
Simulation of the Model
\end_layout

\begin_layout Frame
\begin_inset Argument 4
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Simulation softwares and strategies
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Lot of open sourced and commercial advanced softwares are available for
 the simulation and visualisation of the Model none of which is being being
 for my simulations
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
All codes are written using Fortran95 and all the packages and modules are
 self written.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Simple Euler method is invoked for solving the set of coupled differential
 equations which is later improved using runge-kutta of order 4
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Facility for making an animation of plotting of the simulated data is incorporat
d into the code with the help of gnu plot and ffmpeg.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The complete code and animations are available at https://www.dropbox.com/sh/7bd3h
ueoui1kcfq/AAB2iR21nXP1owC
