Simulations
\end_layout

\begin_layout Frame
\begin_inset Argument 4
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Software used for Simulation
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
While analytic solution can be derived, numerical solution can be derived
 from the coupled differential equations to get an insight of the problem.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Again all codes are written using Fortran95 and all the packages and modules
 are self written.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Runge-kutta of order 4 is invoked for solving the set of coupled differential
 equations.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Facility for making an animation of plotting of the simulated data is incorporat
d into the code with the help of gnu plot and ffmpeg.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
